  "description": {
    "en": {
      "provenance": "imported",
      "value": "Provide technical support with team of legal and gender expert to the MoWCSW to organize inclusive consultations for finalizing new laws on Gender equality (taking an intersectionality approach) : violence against women bill and special opportunity bill in line with the new Constitution and the Political Declaration adopted at CSW 59.\r\n\r\nSupport Government training institutions to integrate GE provisions (including GRB) in their training curriculum and provide trainings to further enhance capacities of Government officials in line with the SDGs."
